rules: Rule1: If player1 has aiming skill, then the prize fund is established.
Rule2: Whenever match1 is resolved, it is not disputed.
Rule3: Under the condition that player1 is disqualified, player1 becomes eligible for the prize.
Rule4: If player1 is disqualified, then player1 is banned.
Rule5: Either player1 is disqualified or the prize fund is established.
Rule6: Whenever player1 is banned, player1 is suspended.
Rule7: Provided that decision1 is upheld, decision1 must have been appealed.
Rule8: If energy drink is available, then the prize fund is established.
Rule9: Either energy drink is available or snack bar is available.
Rule10: Under the condition that player1 has strategy skill, the prize fund is established.

Rule11: Either player1 performed poorly, or if it is not the case that availability of snack bar does not imply prize fund establishment leads to player1 consuming energy drink, then player1 performs well.
Rule12: Either match1 is reviewed, or either match1 is completed, or if it is not the case that either match1 is scheduled on day1 or the prize fund is established, then match1 is scheduled on day2.
Rule13: Either match1 is contested or it is not reviewed.
Rule14: Whenever player1 is registered in the tournament, player1 has aiming skill.
Rule15: Either player1 is registered in the tournament or player2 is registered in the tournament.
Rule16: Under the condition that player1 trained professionally, player1 is qualified for the finals.
Rule17: If player1 hired coach1, then player1 is coached by an expert.
Rule18: Provided that player1 hired coach2, if player1 practiced daily, then player1 trained professionally.
Rule19: Under the condition that player1 paid the entry fee, either player1 hired coach1 or player1 hired coach2.
Rule20: Either player1 is refunded the entry fee or player1 paid the entry fee.
Rule21: Provided that the tournament is compliant with rule1, if player2 is registered in the tournament, then player1 has strategy skill.
Rule22: Under the condition that the tournament is compliant with rule2, if player2 is registered in the tournament, then player1 has strategy skill.
Rule23: Whenever rule1 is enforced, the tournament is compliant with rule1.
Rule24: Either rule1 is enforced or rule2 is enforced.
Rule25: If rule2 is enforced, then the tournament is compliant with rule2.
Rule26: Provided that it is not the case that if player2 is qualified for the finals then player1 is qualified, match1 is disputed.
Rule27: Under the condition that it is not the case that if player2 is qualified for the finals then player1 is qualified, match1 is resolved.
Rule28: Provided that it is not the case that if player1 is suspended then player1 is not eligible for the prize, decision1 is upheld.
Rule29: Under the condition that it is not the case that if player1 is suspended then player1 is not eligible for the prize, it is not the case that decision1 is appealed.
Rule30: Provided that it is not the case that if snack bar is available then the prize fund is established, it is not the case that player1 consumed energy drink.
Rule31: Whenever it is not the case that either match1 is scheduled on day1 or the prize fund is established, it is not the case that match1 is scheduled on day2.
Rule32: Provided that it is not the case that the prize fund is established, player2 is qualified for the finals.
Rule33: Under the condition that it is not the case that the prize fund is established, player1 practiced daily.
